Parliament, Wednesday, 27 January 2021 – Members of the media are advised of the change of time for today’s media briefing on the 2021 State of the Nation Address preparations, led by National Assembly Speaker Ms Thandi Modise and National Council of Provinces Chairperson Mr Amos Masondo.
	
	The briefing will now take place as follows:
	
	DATE: Wednesday, 27 January 2021TIME: 13:00
	VENUE: Virtual Platform
	
	The Media Briefing will also be live on Parliament TV (DSTV Channel 408), streamed live on the Parliament YouTube channel and Twitter page on the links below. You may subscribe to the Parliament YouTube channel to receive instant notification of live feeds.
	
	Twitter: https://twitter.com/ParliamentofRSA
	Facebook: https://facebook.com/ParliamentofRSA
	YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/ParliamentofRSA
	
